        "content": "<p>bakerdb <a href=\"https://github.com/cds-hooks/docs/pull/153#issuecomment-361111390\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/cds-hooks/docs/pull/153#issuecomment-361111390\">commented</a> on <a href=\"https://github.com/cds-hooks/docs/pull/153\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://github.com/cds-hooks/docs/pull/153\">PR #153</a></p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>@kpshek It seems to me that \"patient\" should be OPTIONAL even when pulled within \"context.\"  Looks like #153 makes \"encounter\" optional, but not \"patient.</p>\n</blockquote>",
